media:group.media:title: [Quick Guide] King's ransom
media:group.media:description:
items needed: 
- 1 block of granite of any size
- Regular black full helm, platebody and platelegs/skirt
- bronze med helm and iron chainbody

recommended:
- Be on Regular spellbook or have spellbook swap ready
- 1 law and air rune
- Weight reducing clothing
- Check your bank for an Animate Rock Scroll. If you don’t own it anymore, you’ll get one during the quest.
- 4 empty invent slots

Teleports:
- 3 Camelot
- 1 East Ardy
- 1 Black knight’s fortress [Lassar teleport / cb brace monastery / edgeville / falador]
- 1 quest completion

Quests: Holy Grail, One small Favour, Murder mystery and Black knight’s fortress
skills: 45 Magic and 65 Defence

0:00 intro
1:41 The mansion
4:14 Courthouse
7:40 Keep le Fay
10:16 Freeing Arthur
